Unable to send mail from within Webmail:
============
There was an error sending your message: Failed to add recipient: my send to email address here [SMTP: Invalid response code received from server (code: 550, response: Verification failed for <dlitz2@david-litz.com> No Such User Here Sender verify failed)]

Fix:

https://forums.cpanel.net/threads/unable-to-send-mail-from-within-webmail.106657/

edit the valiases file for the domain and add the user name inside it 

pico /etc/valiases/your-domain.com
replace your-domain.com with domain account that have the probleme
normally you will find the fallowing content 

*: :fail: No Such User Here

chang it to 

*: username

replace replace username with the account username
